# Agent Task Enqueue Demo (extension/OpenClaw)
# Purpose: build a small AgentTaskRequest envelope and append it to a sandboxed
# JSONL file via `agent.send_task`. This is a local-only, file-backed example
# that returns just the task_id.

S core agent

